metadata.name: Celestial Vision
metadata.description:
"Celestial Vision" depicts a beautiful woman in a trance-like state, emerging from mountains and mist beneath a moon and starry sky. The large, detailed face of the woman is the centerpiece of the piece, and her expression is of one in a contemplative and introspective trance.

As you look upon this piece, you are invited to join the woman in her journey of self-discovery, as she gazes inward to behold a vision of what truly matters to her. The celestial setting adds a dreamlike quality, and the mist surrounding her creates a sense of mystery and other-worldliness.

Overall, I hope "Celestial Vision" encourages you to take a moment to reflect on your own values, and embrace the beauty and worth of those who appreciate and support you.
